         <div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Introduction">
               <label>Introduction</label>
               <ab>በስመ፡’’…
                  ንጽሕፍ፡ መቅድመ፡ ሰይፈ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ዘ፯ዕለታት፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ብክሙ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በከመ፡ አተውክሙ፡
                  ውስተ፡ ቤተ፡ አብርሃም፡…</ab>
               <note>quoted after <ref type="mss" target="ESktm012"></ref></note>
            </div>
            
            <!-- The following textparts based on weekdays are in accordance with BAVet89#ms_1 (MV - 2017-08-01) -->
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Monday">
               <label>Praise for Monday</label>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="SalamMonday"> <!--present in BLorient525 and ESktm012, probably also in other mss DR 2018-01-18-->
                  <note>Part of the prayer for Monday, the first verse is identical in <ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient525"/>
                     and <ref type="mss" corresp="ESktm012"/>, then possibly diverging.</note>
                  <ab>ሰላም፡ ለአብ፡ ነቅዓ፡ ዘይት፡ ምሕርት፡ ጥሉል።</ab>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="PrayerMonday"> <!--present in BLorient525 and ESktm012, probably also in other mss DR 2018-01-18-->
                  <note>Part of the prayer for Monday, following <ref target="#SalamMonday"/>. The beginning in <ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient525"/>
                     and <ref type="mss" corresp="ESktm012"/> is not identical, but very similar.</note>
                  <ab>በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS10171Wright"/>
                     መለኮተ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ፍጽምት፡ አሐቲ፡ ስምረት፡ ወሠለስቱ፡ <del rend="erasure"/>
                     አካል፡ በዋህድ፡ ጽምረት፡ ፩መንበር፡ በ፩ህላዌ፡</ab>
               </div>
              
            </div>
